@startuml UML_Komponentendiagramm_Sollkonzept
!theme plain
title CLI Tool Architektur - Komponentendiagramm (UML Standard)

left to right direction
skinparam componentStyle uml2
skinparam linetype polyline
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
skinparam nodesep 90
skinparam ranksep 110
skinparam ArrowFontSize 11
skinparam ComponentFontSize 13
skinparam PackageFontSize 14

actor "Nutzer" as User

package "Presentation Layer" {
    component "Prompt Service\n@clack/prompts" as Prompt
    component "CLI Kernel\noclif" as CLI
}

package "Business Logic Layer" {
    component "Config Manager\nProjectConfig" as Config
    component "Project Generator\nOrchestrator" as Generator
    component "Template Engine\nEJS" as Template
}

package "Infrastructure Layer" {
    component "File System\nfs/promises" as FS
    component "Automation Module\nexeca" as Auto
}

artifact "Generated Project" as ProjectArtifact

interface "User Prompts" as IUserPrompts
interface "Configuration" as IConfiguration
interface "Template Rendering" as ITemplate
interface "File Operations" as IFileOps
interface "Automation Tasks" as IAutomation

' Layout-Hilfen
Prompt -[hidden]right-> CLI
CLI -[hidden]right-> Config
Config -[hidden]down-> Generator
Generator -[hidden]right-> Template
Template -[hidden]down-> FS
FS -[hidden]down-> Auto
ProjectArtifact -[hidden]right-> IFileOps

User --> Prompt : Interaktion
Prompt ..> CLI : Eingaben

Prompt - IUserPrompts
CLI ..> IUserPrompts : nutzt

CLI ..> Config : Konfiguration
Config - IConfiguration
Generator ..> IConfiguration : nutzt

Generator ..> Template : Templates
Template - ITemplate

Generator ..> FS : Dateien
Template ..> IFileOps : Ausgabe
FS - IFileOps

Generator ..> Auto : Setup
Auto - IAutomation

FS --> ProjectArtifact : schreibt
Auto --> ProjectArtifact : initialisiert

note bottom of Generator
Koordiniert die Generierung
und delegiert an Infrastrukturmodule.
end note

legend bottom
== UML-Notation ==
component: Modul/Systembaustein
interface: angebotene Schnittstelle
artifact: erzeugtes Ergebnis
..>: Abhaengigkeit
-->: Beziehung/Ablauf
endlegend

@enduml